![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/56a6e0f0-3ba2-4ac8-84c0-5f600059ad38/23187.jpg)

Get ready for a new era of playtime as Pixar unveils the first teaser for Toy Story 5. The brief but thrilling look reunites audiences with beloved heroes Woody (Tom Hanks) and Buzz Lightyear (Tim Allen), alongside Jessie (Joan Cusack) and the rest of the gang. This time, the toys face their most modern threat yet: technology.

The teaser introduces a new character, Lilypad, a high-tech smart tablet voiced by Greta Lee, whose arrival signals a major challenge to the classic toys' place in a child's world.

